  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### How these savings are computed\n\nEvery call served by the **local Ollama models** (via the LiteLLM gateway, #102) is metered per token in\n`litellm_gateway_tokens_total`. These panels price those same tokens at what public hosted APIs would have\ncharged, then subtract actual gateway spend for local models ($0 \u2014 they run on your own hardware):\n\n| Reference model | Input $/1M | Output $/1M | Source (checked 2026-07-17) |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| GPT-4o mini | $0.15 | $0.60 | OpenAI pricing |\n| Gemini 2.5 Flash | $0.30 | $2.50 | Google/OpenRouter pricing |\n| Claude Haiku 4.5 | $1.00 | $5.00 | Anthropic pricing |\n| Claude Sonnet 5 | $3.00 | $15.00 | Anthropic pricing ($2/$10 intro through 2026-08-31) |\n\n**Read the budget tier (4o-mini / Flash / Haiku) as the honest comparison** \u2014 these small local models\n(gemma3:1b, codegemma:2b, phi4-mini-reasoning) are budget-tier replacements, not Sonnet-class. The\nSonnet line is the upper bound if the same traffic had gone to a mid-tier hosted model. Hosted calls\nthat actually go through the gateway (claude-sonnet) are excluded from savings and appear as real\nspend on the AI \u2014 Consumption & Cost dashboard. Not counted here: electricity, hardware, and the\nquality gap between a 1B local model and a hosted frontier model \u2014 this measures API-bill avoidance only.\nPrices are constants in the panel queries: update them there when providers change pricing."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Saved (24h) vs GPT-4o mini",
      "description": "What the last 24h of local-model tokens would have cost on GPT-4o mini ($0.15/$0.6 per 1M in/out), minus actual local spend ($0).",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "mimir"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "currencyUSD",
          "decimals": 4
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "textMode": "value_and_name"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 8
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "mimir"
          },
          "expr": "((sum(increase(litellm_gateway_tokens_total{type=\"prompt\",model=~\"ollama_chat/.+\"}[24h])) * 0.15 + sum(increase(litellm_gateway_tokens_total{type=\"completion\",model=~\"ollama_chat/.+\"}[24h])) * 0.6) / 1e6 - (sum(increase(litellm_gateway_spend_usd_total{model=~\"ollama_chat/.+\"}[24h])) or vector(0))) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "GPT-4o mini",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
